1
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:12,875
Vampires will never beat Devils.

2
00:00:12,958 --> 00:00:14,708
[VAMPIRES yelp]

3
00:00:14,791 --> 00:00:16,166
[VAMPIRE 12C groaning]

4
00:00:16,250 --> 00:00:17,583
How pathetic.

5
00:00:17,666 --> 00:00:21,250
They must really believe
they can take over the world.

6
00:00:21,333 --> 00:00:23,375
[VAMPIRES groan]

7
00:00:23,458 --> 00:00:25,083
[VAMPIRE 12E screams]

8
00:00:25,166 --> 00:00:28,541
All right, that's enough
screwin' around!

9
00:00:28,625 --> 00:00:33,125
[SHIKI laughs] I think it's
time for a little punishment!

10
00:00:33,208 --> 00:00:34,708
[VAMPIRES screaming]

11
00:00:34,791 --> 00:00:37,125
[ROEN laughs, whistles]

12
00:00:42,041 --> 00:00:43,208
[VAMPIRE 12I gasps]

13
00:00:43,291 --> 00:00:45,541
[VAMPIRES scream]

14
00:00:45,625 --> 00:00:48,083
Get out of my way!

15
00:00:48,166 --> 00:00:49,041
[VAMPIRE 12L groans]

16
00:00:49,125 --> 00:00:50,583
[LINDO]
Ritsuka!

17
00:02:32,166 --> 00:02:35,208
Stop! Let go of me!

18
00:02:43,250 --> 00:02:44,541
[NESTA groans]

19
00:02:45,083 --> 00:02:46,500
[JEK]
Lord Nesta!

20
00:02:46,583 --> 00:02:48,958
You'll pay for that!

21
00:02:49,041 --> 00:02:50,041
[RITSUKA screams]

22
00:02:50,125 --> 00:02:51,208
I've had enough of you
and your games.

23
00:02:51,291 --> 00:02:53,291
No!

24
00:02:55,833 --> 00:02:57,125
[JEK]
Lord Nesta.

25
00:02:57,208 --> 00:03:00,958
The moon is high. It's time
to prepare for the rite.

26
00:03:10,375 --> 00:03:14,916
[gasping] Stop!
Get away from me!

27
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,666
[NESTA chuckles]

28
00:03:16,750 --> 00:03:20,958
Now relax and give in
to the sweet ecstasy.

29
00:03:22,875 --> 00:03:24,916
[RITSUKA screams]

30
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:25,625
[whistles]

31
00:03:25,708 --> 00:03:27,791
[groans]

32
00:03:29,958 --> 00:03:31,166
[ROEN]
I will do what I must

33
00:03:31,250 --> 00:03:34,416
to make the will of
my master a reality.

34
00:03:34,500 --> 00:03:37,083
Damn you, you filthy mongrel!

35
00:03:37,166 --> 00:03:38,750
[RITSUKA gasping]

36
00:03:38,833 --> 00:03:40,375
[JEK]
Get back here!

37
00:03:49,333 --> 00:03:52,041
It's okay. We're going
to keep you safe.

38
00:03:52,125 --> 00:03:53,833
But how?

39
00:03:55,958 --> 00:03:57,791
[JEK]
This isn't any of your business.

40
00:03:57,875 --> 00:04:00,333
She belongs to Lord Nesta now.

41
00:04:00,416 --> 00:04:02,375
[LINDO]
Over my dead body she does.

42
00:04:02,458 --> 00:04:03,833
Oh, is that a threat?

43
00:04:03,916 --> 00:04:07,041
Or are you volunteering,
you pathetic dhampir?

44
00:04:07,125 --> 00:04:08,250
Take her.

45
00:04:08,333 --> 00:04:09,833
Yeah.

46
00:04:15,916 --> 00:04:19,583
Rem. I'm really scared.

47
00:04:19,666 --> 00:04:23,583
[REM] It's okay.
You're out of danger now.

48
00:04:23,666 --> 00:04:25,333
Thank goodness.

49
00:04:27,666 --> 00:04:30,583
Wait, what?

50
00:04:30,666 --> 00:04:35,208
When all this is over, there's
something I need to tell you.

51
00:04:37,291 --> 00:04:39,791
You'll be safe with me.

52
00:04:41,458 --> 00:04:44,208
By the sacred name,
you will obey me.

53
00:04:44,291 --> 00:04:47,083
Oh ye who lurk in darkness,
begone from here--

54
00:04:47,166 --> 00:04:48,333
[JEK grunts]

55
00:04:50,333 --> 00:04:53,041
Keep your filthy
hands off of me!

56
00:04:53,125 --> 00:04:54,875
[LINDO grunts]

57
00:04:54,958 --> 00:04:57,250
You disgust me!
How could you betray the man

58
00:04:57,333 --> 00:04:59,000
whose blood runs
through your veins?

59
00:04:59,083 --> 00:05:02,291
You turned on your own father!

60
00:05:02,375 --> 00:05:04,250
I have no father.

61
00:05:04,333 --> 00:05:05,458
[JEK]
You fool.

62
00:05:05,541 --> 00:05:07,333
It won't be long until
you're on your knees

63
00:05:07,416 --> 00:05:10,750
begging for the mercy
of Lord Nesta.

64
00:05:10,833 --> 00:05:13,500
No one can defy his
overwhelming power.

65
00:05:13,583 --> 00:05:18,416
So just give up.
Stop this ridiculous fight.

66
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:20,333
Looks like you're
the fool now.

67
00:05:20,416 --> 00:05:23,916
After what you did to Ritsuka,
I will make you all pay.

68
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:26,416
Ha! Just how stupid
can you be?

69
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:28,291
A dhampir is no match
for a vampire.

70
00:05:28,375 --> 00:05:29,958
I could destroy you in a second.

71
00:05:30,041 --> 00:05:31,458
[LINDO groans]

72
00:05:31,541 --> 00:05:32,000
[JEK grunts]

73
00:05:32,083 --> 00:05:33,916
[LINDO screams]

74
00:05:35,666 --> 00:05:37,416
[JEK]
Die!

75
00:05:46,208 --> 00:05:49,750
Damn. What've you done?

76
00:05:52,125 --> 00:05:56,583
[LINDO]
Begone from here, forevermore!

77
00:06:03,583 --> 00:06:06,291
[JEK groans]

78
00:06:08,958 --> 00:06:11,375
Lord Nesta...

79
00:06:16,125 --> 00:06:19,041
[JEK]
My everything...

80
00:06:20,708 --> 00:06:23,291
Such a disappointment.

81
00:06:24,208 --> 00:06:25,458
Eat some of this!

82
00:06:25,541 --> 00:06:26,416
[VAMPIRE 12N screams]

83
00:06:26,500 --> 00:06:28,916
[laughs] How about some more?

84
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:31,291
[VAMPIRES screaming]

85
00:06:32,083 --> 00:06:34,125
[VAMPIRES scream]

86
00:06:34,625 --> 00:06:36,250
[yells]

87
00:06:36,583 --> 00:06:37,833
[gasps]

88
00:06:42,166 --> 00:06:47,250
[NESTA]
My son. My one and only son.

89
00:06:47,333 --> 00:06:50,166
Shut up! You think I care?

90
00:06:50,250 --> 00:06:52,375
[gasps]

91
00:06:52,458 --> 00:06:55,083
[NESTA] Do you have any
idea how long I've waited

92
00:06:55,166 --> 00:06:59,166
to see you here? Don't you know
how important you are to me?

93
00:06:59,250 --> 00:07:02,375
No. I guess you wouldn't.

94
00:07:05,041 --> 00:07:07,958
[NESTA]
The only love I have ever known.

95
00:07:08,041 --> 00:07:13,666
The true love of my life
was your mother, Marta.

96
00:07:14,958 --> 00:07:19,333
[NESTA] My poor, sweet Marta.
So kind and gentle.

97
00:07:19,416 --> 00:07:21,083
But in the end,
it was her kindness

98
00:07:21,166 --> 00:07:24,500
that destroyed her and
broke her son's heart.

99
00:07:24,583 --> 00:07:27,125
I hoped one day we
could be a family.

100
00:07:27,208 --> 00:07:29,750
Just the three of us,
together forever.

101
00:07:29,833 --> 00:07:33,708
[LINDO] The three of us.
Together forever?

102
00:07:33,791 --> 00:07:35,125
Yes.

103
00:07:35,208 --> 00:07:37,958
But I need the grimoire to
make that dream come true.

104
00:07:38,041 --> 00:07:41,458
We will never be free so long
as they are still around.

105
00:07:41,541 --> 00:07:43,750
That's why I need
your help, son.

106
00:07:43,833 --> 00:07:45,791
I need you to get
me the grimoire,

107
00:07:45,875 --> 00:07:49,875
so that I can destroy the
devils once and for all.

108
00:07:49,958 --> 00:07:51,125
[LINDO exhales]

109
00:07:51,208 --> 00:07:53,750
At last, you and I will
control the dark realm.

110
00:07:53,833 --> 00:07:55,875
And we can do as we please.

111
00:07:55,958 --> 00:07:58,875
We could even bring
your mother back.

112
00:08:00,791 --> 00:08:06,916
Come. Take your place
beside me, my son.

113
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,666
Father...

114
00:08:12,250 --> 00:08:13,458
[gasps]

115
00:08:15,625 --> 00:08:17,416
Lindo!

116
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:19,708
[NESTA]
The day I've waited for is here.

117
00:08:19,791 --> 00:08:23,791
My one and only son has
finally come home to me.

118
00:08:23,875 --> 00:08:25,541
He's lying to you!
Please, stop!

119
00:08:25,625 --> 00:08:27,500
You cannot trust him!

120
00:08:29,291 --> 00:08:32,166
[NESTA] I always knew you
would fight alongside me.

121
00:08:32,250 --> 00:08:35,625
Because you hate the
devils too, don't you?

122
00:08:40,625 --> 00:08:43,666
Now, we can't be stopped.

123
00:08:53,333 --> 00:08:56,583
Now, we can't be stopped.

124
00:09:03,791 --> 00:09:06,541
[NESTA laughs]

125
00:09:11,416 --> 00:09:13,250
[LINDO grunts]

126
00:09:13,333 --> 00:09:16,500
[NESTA groaning]

127
00:09:18,166 --> 00:09:22,166
I'd rather die than fight
alongside you. Dad!

128
00:09:22,250 --> 00:09:25,041
[screams]

129
00:09:28,875 --> 00:09:31,375
[NESTA groaning]

130
00:09:34,083 --> 00:09:38,208
[screams]

131
00:09:48,458 --> 00:09:50,375
It's done.

132
00:09:50,458 --> 00:09:52,916
[VAMPIRES whimper]

133
00:09:56,125 --> 00:09:58,000
[MAGE, SHIKI, URIE, ROEN gasp]

134
00:10:00,166 --> 00:10:02,291
[RITSUKA]
You're okay!

135
00:10:04,750 --> 00:10:06,666
Ritsuka!

136
00:10:07,250 --> 00:10:10,791
Well, it looks like the exorcist
stole our thunder after all.

137
00:10:10,875 --> 00:10:12,458
I'll allow it this once.

138
00:10:12,541 --> 00:10:16,083
That standoff sent
chills down my spine.

139
00:10:18,541 --> 00:10:20,625
Hey Rem. What's up?

140
00:10:20,708 --> 00:10:22,583
[NESTA chuckles]

141
00:10:22,666 --> 00:10:24,166
[BOTH gasp]

142
00:10:24,250 --> 00:10:27,083
[NESTA] You couldn't honestly
believe that a dhampir

143
00:10:27,166 --> 00:10:32,625
could kill me. Come, now.
I'm a king, after all.

144
00:10:38,250 --> 00:10:42,208
[NESTA laughs]

145
00:10:42,291 --> 00:10:43,791
No way!

146
00:10:43,875 --> 00:10:45,458
[SHIKI] But the legend
said, if you pierce

147
00:10:45,541 --> 00:10:49,791
the Vampire King's heart
he'll die writhing in agony.

148
00:10:49,875 --> 00:10:51,375
He's hidden it.

149
00:10:51,458 --> 00:10:52,458
[URIE]
His heart?

150
00:10:52,541 --> 00:10:53,583
[ROEN]
If they were that easy to kill

151
00:10:53,666 --> 00:10:55,250
someone would've already
done it by now.

152
00:10:55,333 --> 00:10:57,375
I've heard their ancestors
possessed some sort

153
00:10:57,458 --> 00:11:00,750
of special ability. That must be
the secret of their longevity.

154
00:11:00,833 --> 00:11:02,541
Tell us where it is!

155
00:11:02,625 --> 00:11:04,041
Even if I did,

156
00:11:04,125 --> 00:11:07,916
you devils aren't smart enough
to find a way to stop me.

157
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,083
[REM grunts]

158
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:15,250
[yells]

159
00:11:15,333 --> 00:11:17,791
[ALL groaning]

160
00:11:18,916 --> 00:11:20,166
[RITSUKA yelps]

161
00:11:20,250 --> 00:11:21,000
[ALL groaning]

162
00:11:21,083 --> 00:11:22,125
[screams]

163
00:11:22,208 --> 00:11:24,000
Ritsuka!

164
00:11:24,083 --> 00:11:24,541
[REM groans]

165
00:11:24,625 --> 00:11:25,666
[LINDO groans]

166
00:11:25,750 --> 00:11:27,208
[REM groaning]

167
00:11:27,291 --> 00:11:29,083
No! You're hurt!

168
00:11:29,166 --> 00:11:32,416
[chuckles] Just give up.

169
00:11:32,500 --> 00:11:34,458
The grimoire is mine.

170
00:11:34,541 --> 00:11:37,583
And with its power,
I will control the world.

171
00:11:37,666 --> 00:11:39,875
Isn't it a pity that you'll
never experience it

172
00:11:39,958 --> 00:11:45,291
because you'll be dead! [laughs]

173
00:11:45,375 --> 00:11:49,541
It's no use. Why are you making
it harder on yourselves?

174
00:11:49,625 --> 00:11:53,333
There is nothing you
can do to stop me.

175
00:11:54,375 --> 00:11:59,500
[RITSUKA] All this pain...
All this fighting...

176
00:11:59,583 --> 00:12:02,125
All because of the grimoire!

177
00:12:05,125 --> 00:12:08,000
[RITSUKA]
My whole life changed.

178
00:12:08,083 --> 00:12:10,875
So many people died.

179
00:12:10,958 --> 00:12:12,750
And for what?

180
00:12:12,833 --> 00:12:16,875
Because of some horrible
power that lies within me?

181
00:12:19,125 --> 00:12:22,416
[RITSUKA]
No. That's not fair.

182
00:12:22,500 --> 00:12:24,333
I won't let this control me.

183
00:12:24,416 --> 00:12:28,750
I'm sick of people I care
about paying the price.

184
00:12:28,833 --> 00:12:31,833
If this is my destiny,
then this is my fight.

185
00:12:31,916 --> 00:12:34,500
And I'm not running
away anymore.

186
00:12:34,583 --> 00:12:36,916
So if the grimoire
lies within me,

187
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:39,375
then I get to choose
what happens to it.

188
00:12:39,458 --> 00:12:41,458
It's my choice.

189
00:12:44,166 --> 00:12:50,125
[clock chimes]

190
00:12:51,958 --> 00:12:53,458
[REM gasps]

191
00:12:56,625 --> 00:13:00,375
[BOTH gasping]

192
00:13:00,458 --> 00:13:02,208
Ritsuka?

193
00:13:03,958 --> 00:13:06,666
[RITSUKA] And I choose
to use its power myself.

194
00:13:06,750 --> 00:13:08,958
I am going to protect them all!

195
00:13:09,041 --> 00:13:11,750
[NESTA gasping]

196
00:13:15,083 --> 00:13:16,250
[RITSUKA gasps]

197
00:13:22,083 --> 00:13:23,250
[RITSUKA]
Uh?

198
00:13:31,625 --> 00:13:33,458
Azuna...

199
00:13:36,083 --> 00:13:38,958
[gasping]

200
00:13:48,083 --> 00:13:49,791
[NESTA groans]

201
00:14:13,541 --> 00:14:15,250
[NESTA grunts]

202
00:14:20,333 --> 00:14:22,916
[heartbeats]

203
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,666
[RITSUKA]
Even the most feared vampire

204
00:14:24,750 --> 00:14:29,791
who thrives in darkness is
terrified to face his own death.

205
00:14:29,875 --> 00:14:34,708
That's enough.
His reign ends now.

206
00:14:34,791 --> 00:14:36,833
It's time you find
your humanity,

207
00:14:36,916 --> 00:14:39,541
and leave this world behind.

208
00:14:39,625 --> 00:14:41,791
Rest in peace.

209
00:14:42,750 --> 00:14:47,416
[NESTA screams]

210
00:14:57,416 --> 00:14:59,208
[NESTA groaning]

211
00:14:59,291 --> 00:15:00,625
[RITSUKA gasps]

212
00:15:07,166 --> 00:15:10,583
[screams]

213
00:15:28,833 --> 00:15:30,583
Uh! No!

214
00:15:32,458 --> 00:15:34,916
Ritsuka. Come on.

215
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:36,875
Please, wake up!

216
00:15:40,083 --> 00:15:42,000
Thank you.

217
00:15:42,083 --> 00:15:46,500
I'm here for you.
I won't let go.

218
00:15:51,708 --> 00:15:55,500
I have to be honest. I've
never seen Rem like this.

219
00:15:55,583 --> 00:15:56,125
Yeah.

220
00:15:56,208 --> 00:15:57,458
Aw, man.

221
00:15:57,541 --> 00:16:00,000
I'm quite depressed now
that the grimoire's gone.

222
00:16:00,083 --> 00:16:04,250
[sniffs] Not to mention
the scent's almost gone too.

223
00:16:04,333 --> 00:16:07,625
Patience gentlemen,
we've got time.

224
00:16:07,708 --> 00:16:11,458
Let's see. Only a 615 year wait.

225
00:16:11,541 --> 00:16:12,625
[ROEN]
How unfortunate.

226
00:16:12,708 --> 00:16:16,000
Lord Maksis will be
rather disappointed.

227
00:16:16,083 --> 00:16:19,541
I suppose I'll just have to
search for something else.

228
00:16:24,166 --> 00:16:25,750
[REM]
When we first met,

229
00:16:25,833 --> 00:16:29,916
I didn't know it, but our fate
had already been sealed.

230
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:33,916
I felt something that I didn't
really know how to explain.

231
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:38,583
And, I was afraid you
wouldn't feel the same way.

232
00:16:38,666 --> 00:16:39,791
But...

233
00:16:41,375 --> 00:16:42,666
[gasps]

234
00:16:43,791 --> 00:16:48,250
I can't keep it to
myself anymore.

235
00:16:48,333 --> 00:16:51,250
I love you, Ritsuka.

236
00:16:56,583 --> 00:16:58,500
I'm glad.

237
00:16:58,583 --> 00:17:00,291
I love you.

238
00:17:07,458 --> 00:17:10,541
[RITSUKA cries]

239
00:17:20,666 --> 00:17:22,958
[REM]
Now that the grimoire is gone,

240
00:17:23,041 --> 00:17:26,916
there's no reason for me to
continue living in this world.

241
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:28,916
Come back with me.

242
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:30,291
[gasps]

243
00:17:30,375 --> 00:17:32,750
We can be together.

244
00:17:32,833 --> 00:17:35,541
We could have a life we've
only dreamed about.

245
00:17:35,625 --> 00:17:38,000
In the demon world.

246
00:17:38,083 --> 00:17:43,041
♪♪♪

247
00:17:43,125 --> 00:17:47,416
[RITSUKA, LINDO, REM]
♪ Dance with destinies ♪

248
00:17:47,500 --> 00:17:53,000
♪ High up in the sky
Enclosed by millions of stars ♪

249
00:17:53,083 --> 00:18:02,333
♪ How our paths ever crossed
Miraculous we're all here ♪

250
00:18:02,416 --> 00:18:07,541
♪ Now I need to tell the truth
What I feel inside my heart ♪

251
00:18:07,625 --> 00:18:16,125
♪ I love you forever and ever ♪

252
00:18:21,500 --> 00:18:24,791
[LINDO] ♪ I can see she's
found her wings ♪

253
00:18:24,875 --> 00:18:31,208
♪ And it's time for her fly ♪

254
00:18:31,291 --> 00:18:34,750
♪ I'll always be there
to protect her ♪

255
00:18:34,833 --> 00:18:41,083
♪ Now I know
I can do so from afar ♪

256
00:18:41,166 --> 00:18:46,083
I'll keep her safe. I swear.
That's how I'll show my love.

257
00:18:47,541 --> 00:18:51,750
[RITSUKA, REM]
♪ Dance in a sweet dream ♪

258
00:18:51,833 --> 00:18:57,333
